title: INSIGHT: Happy 92nd to UK Queen
text:
INSIGHT: Happy 92nd to UK Queen 9:49pm IST - 01:11 
Gun salutes have marked the 92nd birthday of Britain's Queen Elizabeth, the world's oldest and longest-reigning monarch. Relive some of her most memorable moments caught on camera. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
